# Personal Claude Code Configuration Template

This is a **template** for personal Claude Code settings. Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` in the project root to customize your own development preferences without affecting the team's shared configuration.

```bash
# To use this template:
cp CLAUDE.local.md.template CLAUDE.local.md
# Then edit CLAUDE.local.md with your personal preferences
```

**Note**: `CLAUDE.local.md` is in `.gitignore` and will never be committed to the repository.

